<P>
   SUPERLOTTO-CHANGE (Los Angeles) _ Come Wednesday, picking a
winning ticket in California's SuperLotto will be a lot easier,
when a new game modeled after multi-state powerball lotteries
begins. While the odds of winning something will be greater, the
odds winning the bigger jackpots are getting much worse. By Steve
Carney. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California state
news files.)
