here Saturday night and scheduled dinner meeting with Russian
President Vladimir Putin. President Clinton is here for two days of
high-level meetings with Russian President Vladimir Putin on a
variety of issues, including nuclear weapons reductions. But in the
weeks and days leading up to the summit, the Clinton administration
has greatly reduced its aspirations about what the meetings will
