u p BC-GORE-RUSSIA0604-COX     06-03 1170
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GORE-RUSSIA0604-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Gore has stake in Russia's future
 &HT;    By Ken Foskett
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ President Clinton is in Moscow this weekend for
what may be the last summit of his presidency with Russian leaders.
</P>
